4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists with no prior experience. The bootcamp lasts 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 students per class. Participants gain essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while mastering cloud security and penetration testing. They also learn cyber threat intelligence and risk management strategies. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The program's syllabus is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop